cs.DL, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.CY, cs.HC

The paper discusses citation indexing, research evaluation, and scientific disciplines, which are all related to digital libraries (cs.DL) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of science mapping tools such as CiteSpace also falls under the category of social and information networks (cs.SI). The paper also touches on the impact of Garfield's ideas on the broader environment in which research plays a role, which could be related to cybernetics (cs.CY) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
